Generates a fear map based on the provided threat sources

Paramaters:
playersKnown : A list of threat sources provided by the
Returns: A 2D array of integers with appropriate fear value of ending a turn on a tile

func generateDangerMap(playersKnown){
map = new 2D array();
for each source in Sources
	source.addRangedThreat(map)   or  source.addMeleeThreat(map)
	
end for
// Base map is produced
// Add unit specific modifiers 
Unit.FearMapModifier(map)

return map

}

Threat Sources:
2 Types:
	Ranged: Fixed value around range, and decreases gradually  
	Melee: Essentially a ranged source with a range of 1



